MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 268

RESERVING FOR MUNICIPAL CEMETERY SITE PURPOSES CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND SITUATED AT BABAK, ISLAND GARDEN CITY OF SAMAL, PROVINCE OF DAVAO DEL NORTE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale or any other forms of disposition, and reserve for Municipal Cemetery site purposes, under the administration of the Local Government Unit, Island Garden City of Samal, subject to private rights, if any there be, certain parcels of land of the public domain situated in Babak, Island Garden City of Samal, Province of Davao del Norte, Island of Mindanao, and more particularly described as follows;

Lot 75, Pls-566-D

A PARCEL, OF LAND, Lot 75, Pls-566-D, situated in the Municipality of Babak, Island Garden City of Samal, Davao del Norte.

Bounded on the N., along line 5-6 by Lot 77, on the E., along line 6-1 by Lot 74; on the S., along line 1-2 by Lot 76, and W., along lines 2-3-4-5 by Lot 77, all of Pls-566-D.

Beginning from point marked “1” on plan being N. 78-49′ W., 1489.73 m. from BLLM # 1, Pls-566-D, Samal Public Land Subdivision, thence.

101.72 m. to point 2;

41.99 m. to point 3;

66.20 m. to point 4;

90.04 m. to point 5;

97.39 m. to point 6;

141.68 m. to point 1;

Containing an area of NINE THOUSAND EIGHT HUNDRED FORTY FOUR (9,844) SQUARE METERS, more or less, all corners are “PLS” Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15 x 60 cm. Bearings true. Date of Original Survey December 10, 1956 to September 18, 1957 and approved on December 28, 1965 and the survey duly executed by Deputy Public Land Surveyor Bonifacio Tamayo.

Lot 76, Pls-566-D

A PARCEL OF LAND, Lot 76, Pls-566-D, situated in the Municipality of Babak, Island Garden City of Samal, Davao del Norte.

Bounded on the N., along line 4-1 by Lot 75, on the E., along line 1-2, on the S., along line 2-3 and W., along line 3-4, all of Lot 7, Pls-566-D.

Beginning from the point marked “1” on plan, being No. 78-49’W., 1489.73 m. from BLLM #1, Pls-566-D, thence.

63.15 m. to point 2;

100.97 m. to point 3;

49.15 m. to point 4;

101.72 m. to point 1;

point of beginning.

Containing an area of FIVE THOUSAND SIX HUNDRED FIFTY (5,650) SQUARE METERS, more or less. All corners are “PLS” Cyl. Conc. Mons 15 x 60 cm. Bearings true. Date of Original Survey December 10, 1956 to September 18, 1957 and approved on December 28, 1965 and was executed by Deputy Public Land Surveyor, Bonifacio Tamayo.point of beginning.

The tracts of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable and shall not be subject to occupation, entry, sale, lease, or other disposition until again declared alienable by proclamation of the President.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 30th day of September, in the year of Our Lord, two thousand and two.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

